# Once done this will define
#
#  SLV2_FOUND - system has Slv2
#  SLV2_INCLUDE_DIRS - the Slv2 include directory
#  SLV2_LIBRARIES - Link these to use Slv2
#  SLV2_DEFINITIONS - Compiler switches required for using Slv2
